fields.title: Front-end Web deveoper
fields.jobdesc: We are seeking a skilled and creative Frontend Web Developer to join our dynamic team. The ideal candidate will possess a strong foundation in web development technologies and techniques, with a focus on creating visually appealing and user-friendly interfaces. You will collaborate closely with our design and backend development teams to bring engaging and responsive web experiences to life.
fields.responsibilities:
Collaborate with designers and backend developers to translate wireframes and mockups into interactive web applications.
Develop and maintain efficient, reusable, and high-performance frontend code using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript frameworks.
Implement responsive design principles to ensure seamless user experiences across various devices and screen sizes.
Optimize application performance by identifying bottlenecks and finding solutions to improve loading times and overall responsiveness.
fields.requirements:
Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Web Development, or a related field (or equivalent experience).
Proven experience as a Frontend Web Developer or similar role.
Proficiency in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and related frontend technologies.
Strong experience with frontend frameworks such as React, Angular, or Vue.js.
Familiarity with version control systems (e.g., Git) and collaborative development workflows.
Experience with responsive and mobile-first design principles.

fields.title: Back-end Developer
fields.jobdesc: We are in search of a skilled and motivated Backend Developer to join our dynamic team. The ideal candidate will have a strong background in server-side development, databases, and API integration. You will work closely with our frontend and design teams to architect and build robust and scalable backend systems that power our web applications.
fields.responsibilities:
Collaborate with frontend developers, designers, and other cross-functional teams to design, develop, and maintain efficient backend systems.
Build and maintain APIs for seamless communication between the frontend and backend components of our applications.
Develop secure and scalable server-side logic, handling data storage, user authentication, and application logic.
Design and optimize databases, ensuring efficient data retrieval and storage while maintaining data integrity.
fields.requirements:
Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering, or a related field (or equivalent experience).
Proven experience as a Backend Developer or similar role.
Strong proficiency in server-side programming languages such as Python, Java, Ruby, or Node.js.
Experience with backend frameworks like Django, Flask, Ruby on Rails, or Express.js.
Solid understanding of RESTful API design principles.
Proficiency in database management systems, both SQL (e.g., PostgreSQL, MySQL) and NoSQL (e.g., MongoDB, Redis).
